<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11166&amp;p=127800#p127800"><![CDATA[
At scales like this (1px = 25mm), mitten hands are unavoidable because you can't fit four distinct fingers into four pixels. But at least make a suggestion of a thumb.<br /><br />I'll need some time to look over these pics and see what details to change, as well as expected width of a head side-to-side vs. front-to-back. I might have to strip her down and refine the underlying &quot;doll base&quot;, as some pixel artists call it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Apr 17, 2014 8:45 am</p><hr />
